Aramark Services, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 4:21 PM ET
Commercial Services and Supplies

Company Overview of Aramark Services, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Aramark Services, Inc. provides food, facilities, and uniform services to education, healthcare, business and industry, sports, leisure, and corrections clients in the United States and internationally. It offers food and support services comprising business dining services, such as on-site restaurants, catering, convenience stores, and executive dining rooms; coffee and vending services; and facility management services, including housekeeping, plant operations and maintenance, energy management, laundry and linen, grounds keeping, landscaping, capital program management and commissioning services, and other facility consulting services related to building operations. The company also provi...
Aramark Services, Inc. provides food, facilities, and uniform services to education, healthcare, business and industry, sports, leisure, and corrections clients in the United States and internationally. It offers food and support services comprising business dining services, such as on-site restaurants, catering, convenience stores, and executive dining rooms; coffee and vending services; and facility management services, including housekeeping, plant operations and maintenance, energy management, laundry and linen, grounds keeping, landscaping, capital program management and commissioning services, and other facility consulting services related to building operations. The company also provides banquet and retail services, merchandise sales, and recreational and lodging services in sports, entertainment, and recreational facilities; food and facility services to colleges, universities, and schools; and patient food and nutrition services, retail food services, clinical equipment maintenance, environmental services, strategic/technical services, supply chain management, and central transportation services for the healthcare sector. In addition, it rents, sells, cleans, maintains, and delivers personalized uniform and career apparel, and other textile products on a contract basis for a range of industries, including manufacturing, transportation, construction, restaurants and hotels, healthcare and pharmaceutical, and other industries, as well as walk-off mats, cleaning cloths, and disposable towels. Aramark Services, Inc. was formerly known as ARAMARK Corporation and changed its name to Aramark Services, Inc. in May, 2014. The company was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. Aramark Services, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of ARAMARK Intermediate Holdco Corporation.
